'''Slovakia''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was added to [[BitLife: Life Simulator|BitLife]] in the May 10, 2020 update, alongside [[Algeria]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Bolivia]], [[Croatia]], [[Georgia]], [[Hungary]], [[Jordan]], [[Qatar]], and [[Zimbabwe]]. The only default city is its capital, Bratislava.

